dct_title_s: Map of Minneapolis, Hennepin Co., Minn., 1897. Plate no. 34, Sewer map
dct_description_sm: Cartographic Details: Scale [1:24,000]. 2,000 ft. to 1 in. Relief shown by contours and spot heights. Shows sewers and sewer tunnels, street car lines and railroads, and parks. On verso: "Plate Number 34. Sewer Map." Dimensions: 72 x 47 centimeters
